Subject: [PATCH 24/36] nx503a: ARM: dts: msm: Enable thermal reset feature for
 MSM8974

cherry-pick from a4b5bac31402946ef18be1a45e52e2d1d9184a41

Enable thermal reset feature for MSM8974, where the KTM does
a secure watchdog bite when the temperature of tsens reaches
the preset threshold.
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/NX503A/msm8974.dtsi | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/NX503A/msm8974.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/NX503A/msm8974.dtsi
index 360a707..648ee44 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/NX503A/msm8974.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/NX503A/msm8974.dtsi
@@ -2323,6 +2323,7 @@
 		qcom,poll-ms = <250>;
 		qcom,limit-temp = <60>;
 		qcom,temp-hysteresis = <10>;
+		qcom,therm-reset-temp = <115>;
 		qcom,freq-step = <2>;
 		qcom,freq-control-mask = <0xf>;
 		qcom,core-limit-temp = <80>;
